IN THE HIGH COURT OF PUNJAB AND HARYANA AT CHANDIGARH Civil Writ Petition No.5758 of 1991 (O&M) Date of decision:21.07.2011 G.D.Sharma and others ...Petitioners versus Haryana Kshetriya Gramin Bank, Bhiwani and others ....Respondents CORAM: HON BLE MR. JUSTICE K. KANNAN ---- Present: None. ---- . Whether reporters of local papers may be allowed to see the judgment ? No. . To be referred to the reporters or not ? No. . Whether the judgment should be reported in the digest ? No.

---- K.Kannan, J. (Oral) There is no representation at the time when the matter is called. The writ petition is, accordingly, dismissed for default for non- prosecution. (K. KANNAN) JUDGE .07.2011 sanjeev
